reviewText: Lots of great horror themed bands' videos on here. From live footage from such well known acts as Michale Graves, Dr. Chud's X Ward, and Calabrese. To videos from underground gems such as Under A Nightmare, Lugosi's Morphine, Werevilsdare, Spectemen, Creepersin, Lurking Corpses, and Diemonsterdie. Lots of different features, all horror.
